data.description: Nestled in the gated community of Mira Lago West, this exquisite 2-story floor home features 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a spacious 3-car tandem garage, and an expansive upstairs BONUS room with a LOFT! This home is designed for optimal living, featuring an open floor plan ideal for entertaining guests. As you step into the grand 2-story foyer, you'll be greeted by the elegance of the formal living and dining areas. The expansive kitchen offers plenty of space for storage, food preparation, and entertainment. Adjacent is the inviting large family room with the view of the Marsh and slider access to the back through the breakfast nook. Downstairs, a thoughtfully placed guest bedroom with a full bath and laundry room offer versatility and comfort for guests or multigenerational living arrangements. Upstairs, discover the luxurious master suite, complete with his and her closets and a master bath featuring a separate tiled shower and indulgent garden tub, creating a private oasis for relaxation and rejuvenation.  Secondary bedrooms share a large full bathroom with double vanity & sinks. This home also comes with an enclosed screened in porch from the kitchen and family room that has a beautiful view of the Marsh to enjoy.      Residents of the Mira Lago West community enjoy exclusive access amenities, including a community pool for refreshing dips on sunny days, a basketball court for friendly games and exercise, and convenient nearby boat access to the picturesque Tampa Bay, perfect for water enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Strategically located between the vibrant cities of Tampa and the picturesque coastal towns of Bradenton and Sarasota, this home offers unparalleled convenience with easy access to major thoroughfares such as I-75. Explore the endless recreational opportunities at nearby destinations like the tranquil Little Harbor Resort and Bahia Beach, the expansive EG Simmons Park, and the cultural attractions of Tampa, Pinellas County, and Manatee County.    With its prime location surrounded by a myriad of attractions and activities, don't miss the opportunity to experience the lifestyle of your dreams—schedule your showing today!
